column5: Hi, I booked the 1st week of July at this lake with the (former) Moselle-Natakim outfitter in Quebec. I'm told there is a new owner now called L'aventure du Pro. We went to Lac Ducarny on the same territory the last 2 years, and were looking for a change this year. Any recent advice on walleye and lake trout on this lake? Anyone has dealt with the new owner? Thanks Luc
